01:27:54,920 --> 01:27:55,920
They're married now.

1211
01:27:55,920 --> 01:27:59,760
It's Kori and Topanga, not Kori and us.

1212
01:27:59,760 --> 01:28:00,760
Remember?

1213
01:28:02,760 --> 01:28:03,760
Ma?

1214
01:28:03,760 --> 01:28:06,600
You can't stay here, Kori.

